{"word":"κτίσις","slug":"κτίσις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰτίσις, εως, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κτίζω\">κτίζω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘act of bringing into existence’, <b>creation <a href='B:520 1:20'>Ro 1:20</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘product of a creative act’ <b>creation <a href='B:480 10:6'>Mk 10:6</a>; <a href='B:480 13:19'>13:19</a>; <a href='B:480 16:15'>16:15</a>; <a href='B:520 1:25'>Ro 1:25</a>; <a href='B:520 8:19'>8:19</a>; <a href='B:540 5:17'>2 Cor 5:17</a>; <a href='B:550 6:15'>Gal 6:15</a>; <a href='B:580 1:15'>Col 1:15</a>, <a href='B:580 1:23'>23</a>; <a href='B:650 4:13'>Hb 4:13</a>; <a href='B:650 9:11'>9:11</a>; <a href='B:680 3:4'>2 Pt 3:4</a>; <a href='B:730 3:14'>Rv 3:14</a>.</b> —In special sense of an orderly system or arrangement produced by humans ἀνϑρωπῖνη <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κτίσις\">κτίσις</a> human institution <b><a href='B:670 2:13'>1 Pt 2:13</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κτίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κτίσμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}